Class Link

java.lang.Object
  |

All Implemented Interfaces:

public class Link
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable, java.io.Serializable

Represents a link between servers/computers in a network or, more abstractly, represents a weighted edge in a graph. The Link is undirected.

Author:
Trent Apted
